                    <a href="http://browse.deviantart.com/art/Good-Omens-72751716"><img id="textcontent" style="float:left" src="http://th09.deviantart.net/fs22/200H/f/2007/356/c/2/Good_Omens_by_rhianimated.jpg"/></a>
                    <h3>Good Omens, Neil Gaimen and Terry Pratchett</h3>
                    <p>A book about the end of the world. Demons, angels, the anti-Christ, withfinders, witches, and a book of prophecies, which all manage to get lost and found as the end approaches. It is absolutely hilarious in spite of the whole apocalypse thing. </p>
                    </div>
